---
title: Lentil Panang Curry with Roasted Cauliflower, Green Beans and Brown Rice
description: We're always looking for ways to improve our recipes and when it came to this colourful curry, we felt it needed a little something extra to give it that va va voom. Enter, turmeric roasted cauliflower!  Packed with antioxidants, and vibrant in colour, turmeric adds a delicious depth of flavour to cauliflower, making it the perfect plus one for this curry. Enjoy!
